'''Yinchorri''' was the native language of the [[Yinchorri/Legends|Yinchorri]] species from [[Yinchorr/Legends|Yinchorr]]. Most Yinchorri were fluent in both Yinchorri language and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language. "[[Uhanayih]]" meant "Within World" in the language; "[[rolk-mangir]]" meant "horned death."

